result:
div.padding.high.light(style="padding-top: 6rem")
  
  //- Contents
  div.card.padding-medium.margin
    div.flex.wide.justify-space-between
      h2 Users
      //- Right
      input(type="search")

    table.wide
      thead
        tr
          th Name
          th Account Type
          th Actions
      tbody
        tr(v-for="account in $store.getters.allUsers")
          td {{account.account_name}}
          td {{account.account_type}}
          td
            button(v-if="account.account_type=='USER'") Make Admin
            button(v-if="account.account_type=='ADMIN'") Remove Admin
            button Block User
            button Notify User
